<HEADLINE>
<P>
CLUES FOR COSBY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The collective wits behind the new Cosby show ("The Cosby Mysteries," NBC) had 
better start thinking revisions, revisions, revisions. 
</P>
<P>
 The always wonderful Rita Moreno is wasted in a silly, thoughtless role. Give 
her something to do. Cosby's rapport with kids is well known, but the current 
kiddie bits do nothing but slow the pace. 
</P>
<P>
 W.R. Fitts, West Hollywood 
</P>
