<HEADLINE>
<P>
PALM LATITUDES: VERBATIM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Good skin isn't all sunblock and moisturizer. From A Facelift Is a Bargain, by 
Nola Rocco of the Hidden Garden, a post-op plastic surgery hideaway in Beverly 
Hills. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Rule 1: SLEEP ON YOUR BACK. Sleeping on your face pulls and creases the skin 
... 
</P>
<P>
 Rule 9: KEEP ORCHIDS IN YOUR BEDROOM.Plants give off oxygen in the daytime, 
but orchids give off oxygen at night ... 
</P>
<P>
 Rule 10: AVOID BROAD FACIAL EXPRESSIONS AND THE GNAWING OF FOOD. ... 
exercising the facial muscles may cause wrinkles and expression lines, and be 
especially aware of those forehead "thinking" lines. 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
 Looks like no one got any "thinking" lines wondering if orchids are plants. 
</P>
