<HEADLINE>
<P>
STYLE: FASHION; SUEDE APPEAL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The smell of a brand-new sports car, the taste of a good tequila -- these are 
just two of life's little indulgences.But the feel of suede against the skin is 
something else. Suede is sumptuous, sensuous and, yes, sexy. The message it 
sends is subtle: I'm a touchable tough guy. Far from fragile, it's meant to be 
worn often and with abandon. So relax. Let your suede take a few hard knocks. 
It only gets better with age. 
</P>
<P>
 PRODUCED AND STYLED BY MICHAEL EISENHOWER 
</P>
</TEXT>
