<DOCNO> LA103094-0066 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 093518 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 30, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
