<HEADLINE>
<P>
FAMILY TREE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Regarding your Film Clips item on Ellen Simon, Neil Simon's daughter (Oct. 9): 
</P>
<P>
 Her son Andrew Leland's father, Jon, is alive and well, thank goodness, in 
Northern California. Her second husband, Jeff Bishop, did die in a jogging 
accident, but he wasn't Andrew's dad. 
</P>
<P>
 Signed, 
</P>
<P>
 Andrew's dad's best friend, 
</P>
<P>
 RONA ELLIOT 
</P>
<P>
 Beverly Hills 
</P>
</TEXT>
