SHLOMO GOREN; FOUGHT ISRAELI-PLO ACCORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Shlomo Goren, 77, a former chief rabbi of Israel and an outspoken critic of 
Israeli reconciliation with the PLO. Goren, who served as Israel's chief rabbi 
from 1973 to 1983, was often at the center of controversy.A year ago, he issued 
