Goren's call for disobedience was given special weight because he served as 
chief military chaplain during the 1967 Middle East war, reaching the rank of 
brigadier general. Shortly after the September, 1993 Israel-PLO accord on 
autonomy, Goren said that every Jew was commanded to kill PLO chief Yasser 
