<DATE>
<P>
October 30, 1994, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 8; Column 2; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
44 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Doreen G. Skuse has been appointed director of sales and marketing for the 
Airporter Garden Hotel in Irvine. She came to the hotel from the Doubletree 
Hotel in Rancho Bernardo, and has also been director of sales for the Best 
Western Hotel in Rancho Bernardo. 
</P>
</TEXT>
