<HEADLINE>
<P>
CALIFORNIA ELECTIONS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Times takes a look at all statewide races and offers a complete rundown of 
propositions to be decided on Election Day in Decision '94. Section W. 
</P>
