<TEXT>
<P>
 A 737 jetliner with 137 people aboard was diverted Saturday from Burbank 
Airport to Ontario International Airport when an emergency light on the craft 
indicated a possible steering problem. 
</P>
<P>
 Southwest Airlines Flight 578 from Las Vegas landed safely at 2:43 p.m. at 
