<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Because of an editing error, Lani Guinier was incorrectly identified in "Lone 
Justice" (Oct. 9), about Supreme Court Justice Clarence Thomas, as a Clinton 
nominee for attorney general. She had been nominated for assistant attorney 
general to head the civil-rights division of the Justice Department. 
</P>
